
=================== [ Ionis Users Informations PHP Class ] ===================

A PHP Class to get informations about students in Ionis group :
Isbp, Epitech, Etna, Ipsa, Epita, e-art, Web@cademie, ...


============================== [ Requirement ] ===============================

- PHP >= 5.3
- libssh2-php

================================= [ Usage ] ==================================

1) Initialisation

   $ionis = new IonisInfo($login, $pass);
   where $login is your ionis (exampl_e) and $pass is your unix password.


2) Functions

- Get a login from the uid :
    $ionis->getLogin($uid)

- Get uid, name, group, school, promo from the login :
    $ionis->getUid($login);
    $ionis->getName($login);
    $ionis->getGroup($login);
    $ionis->getSchool($login);
    $ionis->getPromo($login);

- Check the PPP password :
    $ionis->checkPass($login, $pass);
    return true if the password match for the login, false otherwise.

- Update informations files
    $ionis->updateFiles();
    update the informations files. Good idea to put it in a crontab.


3) Example

   See the example.php file.

